OL,2,MPhotographing lightning with a DIY
OL,4,Mlightning trigger
OL,6,CDan Pope
OL,7,CFri 13:50-14:10
OL,8,CStage A
OL,10,GLast year I went on a storm chasing
OL,11,Groad trip, aiming to capture some
OL,12,Gphotos of lightning. I had a DSLR
OL,13,Gcamera, a microcontroller, some wires,
OL,14,Ga light sensor and some spare time.
OL,15,GHow hard could it be to make my own
OL,16,Glightning trigger? And would it even
OL,17,Gwork? A beginner-friendly guide to
OL,18,Gcreating electronics with
OL,19,Glightning-fast reaction times, and an
OL,20,Gexcuse to share some holiday pics.
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
